some times we want to find who write some shity lines!
for this we use blame command!

git blame src/section_3/aliases\ 4               //find who write or modified the last time every line
                                                 //on witch commit?

git blame -L 5,10 src/section_3/aliases\ 4       //just want to see line 5 to 10

git blame -e -L 5,10 src/section_3/aliases\ 4    //-e to see author email

Note: intellij has it on right click,
      git--->annotate with git blame